\id 3JN - Nchane
\h 3 Joŋ
\toc1 Ŋwa wù kiŋgane kintɛde wu Joŋ
\toc2 3 Joŋ
\toc3 3Jo
\mt2 Ŋwa wù kiŋgane kintɛde wu
\mt1 Joŋ
\imt1 Fiɛɛ fì le a Ŋwa wu Joŋ wù kiŋgane kintɛde wunɛ le
\ip Joŋ wunɛ tɛŋe kikwɛɛ ke lɛ chiji kikwɛɛ ki kintaashɛ ki bamii ba mbɛmɛ. Wu gɛ̀ saŋ ŋwa we wù kiŋgane kintɛde wunɛ fɛ muh mu wù fwe wu a kintaashɛ ki bamii ba mbɛmɛ le jee che nyu lɛ Gayu. Wu le wu bɛɛŋsɛ Gayu yi nfih wù wu gɛ̀ nyaa bamii ba mbɛmɛ le. Wu le wu nya tɛ nteefɛ fɛ Gayu le lɛ wu yɛ̂ne kune muh mu wù ba tɛŋe lɛ Diotefɛ nje wu gɛ̀ faŋe ki wu yû jɛ ye le.
\iot Bikwɛɛ bi mwɛɛ mù le a Ŋwa wunɛ le
\io1 1-4 Fɛŋkɛɛ
\io1 5-8 Joŋ bɛɛŋsɛ Gayu
\io1 9-10 Joŋ chunyɛ gee chi Diotefɛ
\io1 11-12 Joŋ bɛɛŋsɛ gee chi Dɛmitiyu
\io1 13-15 Kimɛsɛ
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Le mɛ wù chiji kikwɛɛ wu kintaashɛ ki bamii ba mbɛmɛ. Nsaŋe ŋwa wunɛ fɛ wo le Gayu wù nsaa yaŋ yi shɛ́ŋ. Ŋkoŋe wo yi nchiɛɛŋ le.
\s1 Joŋ bɛɛŋsɛ Gayu
\p 
\v 2 Nsaa yaŋ yi shɛ́ŋ, mbuune lɛ mwɛɛ munchii gɛ̂ɛne chuule a kimbe kuŋ le, wo tɛ̂ɛme yi nyaŋ yi ye le gɛh no ŋkee lɛ wo tɛɛme a kiyo le.
\v 3 Ŋgɛ̀ yu njoŋ baaŋ no booŋ ba bwee besa bamu gɛ̀ fɛsɛ yanɛ bo sɛɛŋ kune no wo lɛme yi kinchiɛɛŋ le bɛ fitele fiuŋ fichii. Nyu nchiɛɛŋ lɛ wo bii kinchiɛɛŋ le.
\v 4 Gɛ fiɛɛ fimi ka nyu yu fì taŋlo fi ge n'yûge njoŋ fede ki n'yuge lɛ booŋ ba le baŋ bii kinchiɛɛŋ le gɛ.
\p 
\v 5 Nsaa yaŋ yi shɛ́ŋ, lɛme chì wo lɛne fɛ booŋ ba bwe wese besabɛŋ le, nchensɛŋ chì fɛ ba le bantolo le, wo lɛne chuule.
\v 6 Ba gɛ̀ sɛɛŋ a kintaashɛ ki bamii ba mbɛmɛ ki yanɛ le kune kiŋkoŋɛ kuŋ. Wo mône ki wo fîih bobaa bamii je yì Nyo goone le yi njiɛnyɛ wuboo le noo.
\v 7 Wo kêe lɛ bo bu akfuuŋ nyu nje jee chi Kletu, bo baaŋ jiŋɛ gɛ nfih wumu a bamii ba le gɛ ba Nyo gɛ.
\v 8 Noo, besabɛŋ kɛme ki bee tôone bobaa bamii, wu lɛ besa bo nyûme bamii ba lɛne yi fiɛɛ le fimimia kune kinchiɛɛŋ.
\s1 Kune Diotefɛ bɛ Dɛmitiyu
\p 
\v 9 Ŋgɛ̀ nsaŋ fiɛɛ fɛ kintaashɛ ki bamii ba mbɛmɛ kena le, geenɛ Diotefɛ wù koŋe ki wu gɛ̂ɛde kikwɛɛ ke fwe, wu gɛ̀ faŋ ki wu yû muh wù le mɛ le.
\v 10 Noo, nlé ŋgê ndoo nto, ŋgîiŋsɛ fiɛɛ fì wu gee finɛ fɛkuu, no wu jiɛnyi wu fiɛge kinfiɛ, wu jɛme jɛ́ yì befe kune besabɛŋ. No wu gee noo, wu baaŋ fuu gɛ bɛ fiɛɛ fiyu gɛ. Wu faŋe tɛ ki wu fîi booŋ ba bwee wese besabɛŋ, wu faŋe tɛ bamii ba koŋe ki ba fî bo lɛ keefɛ ba fî bo gɛ. Nɛ bo doo bo goone ki bo fi bo wu mo wu kuŋ lo bo a kintaashɛ ki bamii ba mbɛmɛ ntɛnɛɛ.
\p 
\v 11 Nsaa yaŋ yi shɛ́ŋ, keefɛ wo bêge fiɛɛ fì befe gɛ. Wo bêge nyume fì joŋe. Muh wù gee fiɛɛ fì joŋe le muh wu Nyo, wu gee fì befe le wu baaŋ Nyo a kɛɛ gɛ.
\p 
\v 12 Dɛmitiyu nyu fie muh bamii bachii bo jɛme mwɛɛ mù njoŋe kune wu, kiŋge ke kì joŋe jɛme tɛ kune wu. Bee tɛ jɛme kune wu. Wo kee lo lɛ fiɛɛ fì bee jɛme kune wu le nchiɛɛŋ.
\s1 N'yɛsɛ
\p 
\v 13 Mbaaŋ ŋkɛme mwɛɛ wesee ki nsâŋ fɛ wo le, geenɛ gɛ ŋkoŋe ki nsâŋ lo bɛ finte fi ŋwa gɛ.
\v 14 N'yɛnɛ lɛ shɛɛ shige nto n'yɛŋ lo wo le, besa wo jɛme muh yɛde muh le bɛ ajii.
\p 
\v 15 Nyiɛgee nyûme fɛ wo le. Nsáa yese besa wo yɛɛse wo le. Yɛ̂sɛ nsáa yese besa wo le yichii muh wu mumwaa wu mumwaa bo le, wo nyâ mɛne.
